{
  "texts": [
    "Many algorithms are available, such as WordPiece, Unigram and Byte-Pair Encoding.",
    "Tokenisation rules differ in many aspects, for example in how they treat punctuation (e.g.",
    "suppression of punctuation, punctuation as separate tokens, etc.",
    "), how they treat prefixes and suffixes, or whether they apply a minimum token length.",
    "The importance of these choices depends on the language."
  ]
}